<lb n="0252a02" ed="Y"/><lb n="0256a01" ed="Y" type="old"/>鄯善</cell><cell>鄯善</cell><cell><title level="m">《漢書》</title>的鄯善</cell></row><row><cell>
<lb n="0252a03" ed="Y"/><lb n="0256a02" ed="Y" type="old"/>緊那羅</cell><cell>緊那羅</cell><cell>不詳</cell></row><row><cell>
<lb n="0252a04" ed="Y"/><lb n="0256a03" ed="Y" type="old"/>震旦漢國</cell><cell>震旦</cell><cell>指北朝</cell></row><row><cell>
<lb n="0252a05" ed="Y"/><lb n="0256a04" ed="Y" type="old"/></cell><cell>羅羅</cell><cell>不詳</cell></row><row><cell>
